text: can you all go through <https://gerrit.hyperledger.org/r/#/q/project:fabric+branch:feature/ca> and abandon any of the now irrelevant change sets based on the mass merge we did last week?

Hi all, I've been reading the protocol spec (<http://hyperledger-fabric.readthedocs.io/en/latest/protocol-spec/#421-userclient-enrollment-process>) and would like to ask on which components are already implemented in the current version of fabric? I am mostly concerned with the security Section 4 and the whole enrolment process. If I am not mistaken I can use the HFC node SDK to register,enroll and give out tcerts to users?
